
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "FilingOfAppeals";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<style>
    body {
        background-image: url('../Content/images/solee.jpg');
        position: auto;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        width: 100%;
    }
</style>

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="offset-7 col-5 mt-5 mb-2">
            <form class="form" action="/Home/Enquiry" method="post">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-info">
                        <div class="text-center" style="font-size:25px; color:aliceblue;">REQUEST A CALL BACK</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="name"><b></b></label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="txtname" name="txtname" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                            @*<span id="message"></span><br>*@
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="email"><B></B></label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="txtemail" name="txtemail" placeholder="Email Address" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="num"><B></B></label>
                            <div class="input-group">
                                <span class="input-group-addon bg-light p-1">+91 </span>
                                <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="txtnumber" name="txtnumber" placeholder="Please Enter Number.." required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg float-right">Get Start</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="bg-light card">
        <h3 class="card-header  text-center bg-info text-white">
            SOLE-PROPRIETORSHIP
        </h3>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-justify">
                Sole proprietorship is a form of business entity where a single individual handles the entire business
                organization. He is the sole recipient of all profits and bearer of all loses. There is no separate law that
                governs sole proprietorship. This is the most easy business entity to establish in India. It doesn’t need its
                own Permanent Account Number (PAN) and the PAN of the owner (Proprietor) acts as the PAN for the
                Sole Proprietorship firm
                Main objective is Open Current Bank Account on the Name of Business so it's a simply firm which is
                enabling doing business in India with Less Compliance and Less Costing. a Sole Proprietorship

            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
    <br>
    <br>



    <div class="bg-light card">
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white ">
            <h2 class="text-left">Process:</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="text-justify">
                For registration of Firm require minimum Entity Proof for open a Current Bank Account.
                We have the following option to take entity proof:
            </div>
            <ol>
                <li>MSME Registration Certificate</li>
                <li>Chartered Accountant Business Certification</li>
                <li>Shop act License</li>
                <li>Business ITR</li>
                <li>GST Registration Certificate</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>

    <div class="bg-light card">
        <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
            <h2 class="text-left"> Documents (Required for Registration)</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <ol>
                <li>Address proof</li>
                <li>Identity proof</li>
                <li>Bank statement</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

